You can simply ask Alexa to control your “lamp”. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “iSCS Sentinel” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “iSCS Sentinel” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “iSCS Sentinel” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “iSCS Sentinel” skill, and you'll be navigated to “iSCS Sentinel” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the lamp.”
“Alexa, turn off the lamp.”
